items.title: Adobe to buy Semrush for $1.9 billion
items.description: Adobe said it would offer $12 per share for Semrush, almost double the latter's closing price of $6.89 on Tuesday, before news of the deal.

items.title: With upcoming ban, Meta begins to notify Australian teens that their accounts will be shut down
items.description: When the ban goes into effect on December 10, Meta will revoke account access for users under the age of 16 in Australia.

items.title: Spotify’s new features let listeners explore the people and stories behind their favorite music
items.description: Spotify new features will showcase who's behind your favorite songs, how music is connected, and what inspired the tunes.

items.title: Onepot AI raises $13M to help make chemical drug creation easier
items.description: Onepot AI is a a company that is home to the small-molecule synthesis lab POT-1.

items.title: Target joins OpenAI’s growing list of retail apps
items.description: OpenAI is pushing deeper into retail, with Target set to debut a new ChatGPT-powered app for shoppers. The app is launching in beta next week.
